title: Central wins region title in road thriller
text: Central wins region title in road thriller File Photo by Noah Schroyer Nov 3, 2023 8 hrs ago Facebook WhatsApp SMS Print Copy article link Save The Central Lions held on to defeat Heritage 35-34 on the road to win the 7-4A region title and capture an undefeated 10-0 regular season. Pictured is quarterback JR Harris.
